- Implement Flink checkpointing for fault tolerance :: DONE
- Join position and diagnostics streams :: DONE
- Add Flink metrics to Grafana dashboard

## Checkpointing
Implemented Flink checkpointing with exactly-once semantics and externalized
checkpoint retention, ensuring fault-tolerant state recovery after job
 failures or cancellations ( EXACTLY_ONCE, RETAIN_ON_CANCELLATION, 30 second intervals)